description:
&lt;p&gt;The Trust is a key member of the NW London Integrated Care System. This exciting position sits on the Trust’s Board and will play an important role in building close links within the system as we move towards formalising our ambitions around the ICS for NW London. Over time, like many ICS’s we will work towards building a group model for which this role will remain an important part.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join us as the Chief Finance Officer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To apply, please submit a CV and cover letter under the appropriate application sections. The closing date for applications is 28th November 2020 with interviews taking place on 7th December 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anna Seeley, Executive Assistant to the Chief Executive Officer on 02033156711&lt;/p&gt;
